1
00:00:51,880 --> 00:00:52,759
Us

2
00:00:53,119 --> 00:00:54,479
The first time we met

3
00:00:54,479 --> 00:00:55,359
You kissed me

4
00:00:55,359 --> 00:00:56,159
And I was fine

5
00:00:56,520 --> 00:00:57,359
How about this time

6
00:00:58,520 --> 00:01:00,520
You try kissing him?

7
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:09,120
Yan Ying is really worried about you

8
00:01:12,519 --> 00:01:14,079
Sorry for troubling you all

9
00:01:16,719 --> 00:01:18,159
How did you even get out?

10
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:20,239
Why are you here?

11
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:21,640
Editor Xu

12
00:01:22,599 --> 00:01:23,840
Just now in the restaurant

13
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:25,519
Didn't Yan Ying already tell you?

14
00:01:25,519 --> 00:01:26,040
Stop pretending

15
00:01:26,719 --> 00:01:28,319
You are a character I created

16
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:30,519
Your personality and dispositions

17
00:01:30,680 --> 00:01:32,599
Even your little quirks, I know them all

18
00:01:34,439 --> 00:01:37,079
Stop exploiting Yan Ying's kindness and soft heart

19
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:39,040
To achieve your goals

20
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:42,799
It seems, Editor Xu

21
00:01:43,239 --> 00:01:44,640
You really misunderstand me

22
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:46,840
Xiao Chengjing

23
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,719
No matter what your intentions are

24
00:01:49,040 --> 00:01:49,680
Let me tell you

25
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:52,319
Your ending with Yan Ying is not a bad one

26
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:53,760
It was predetermined from the start

27
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:55,719
When you infiltrated the General's Mansion

28
00:01:56,319 --> 00:01:57,239
As the author

29
00:01:57,239 --> 00:01:59,599
I never put any obstacles in your way

30
00:02:00,719 --> 00:02:01,079
True

31
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:03,519
You both went through a lot

32
00:02:04,239 --> 00:02:05,799
But the real problem is

33
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:09,400
You never truly tried to understand Yan Ying

34
00:02:13,199 --> 00:02:14,680
I don't understand what you're saying

35
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,319
You will understand

36
00:02:23,599 --> 00:02:24,280
This late at night

37
00:02:24,719 --> 00:02:25,439
Where are you going?

38
00:02:26,479 --> 00:02:27,800
I think I'll just head home

39
00:02:29,319 --> 00:02:31,360
It's pretty convenient anyway

40
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,520
It seems like Editor Xu

41
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:36,120
Doesn't want me to bother you two

42
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,479
He seems really concerned

43
00:02:38,479 --> 00:02:39,800
About the relationship between us

44
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:42,639
Aren't we

45
00:02:43,199 --> 00:02:44,319
Just like siblings?

46
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,879
That's what I thought too

47
00:02:46,879 --> 00:02:47,639
But I'm afraid

48
00:02:48,080 --> 00:02:49,159
Chief Editor Xu wouldn't think the same

49
00:02:49,919 --> 00:02:50,759
Don't talk nonsense

50
00:02:51,400 --> 00:02:52,400
I never thought that way

51
00:02:54,919 --> 00:02:56,199
What Chief Editor Xu means

52
00:02:57,159 --> 00:02:59,319
is that he doesn't mind my relationship with Yan Ying

53
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:01,560
or doesn't want me to disturb you two

54
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:08,719
Both

55
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,159
If that's the case

56
00:03:11,479 --> 00:03:13,159
then why not stay here, brother

57
00:03:13,479 --> 00:03:15,800
I'll take good care of you on Yan Ying's behalf

58
00:03:16,439 --> 00:03:16,879
Alright

59
00:03:17,919 --> 00:03:18,599
Then I shall

60
00:03:19,039 --> 00:03:20,360
graciously accept your offer

61
00:03:22,599 --> 00:03:23,039
After you

62
00:03:23,919 --> 00:03:24,719
Please, you go first

63
00:04:17,839 --> 00:04:18,240
Don’t move

64
00:04:19,319 --> 00:04:19,879
Let me hold you for a moment

65
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:24,160
I see Cheng Jing as an elder brother

66
00:04:24,720 --> 00:04:25,600
The reason

67
00:04:25,959 --> 00:04:26,920
I brought him to meet you

68
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:29,279
was to have him give us his blessings

69
00:04:29,639 --> 00:04:30,040
Hmm

70
00:04:31,639 --> 00:04:32,360
Oh my

71
00:04:33,079 --> 00:04:34,439
All my efforts day in and day out

72
00:04:34,439 --> 00:04:35,560
working like a horse for him

73
00:04:36,519 --> 00:04:37,360
So

74
00:04:37,839 --> 00:04:38,720
don't overthink it

75
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:40,000
Hmm

76
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,920
I understand your intentions

77
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:44,920
Well then

78
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,720
however you treat him in the future

79
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:47,720
I'll treat him the same way

80
00:04:48,519 --> 00:04:49,199
As long as he's willing

81
00:04:49,519 --> 00:04:50,399
I’d even give him a bath

82
00:05:07,839 --> 00:05:08,480
Yan Ying

83
00:05:09,879 --> 00:05:11,120
How do you adjust the water temperature here?

84
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:15,680
Don't go

85
00:05:16,319 --> 00:05:17,000
I'll go

86
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,480
Just wrapped in a towel

87
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:36,279
standing there acting all flirty

88
00:05:36,639 --> 00:05:37,879
He's clearly doing it on purpose

89
00:05:38,639 --> 00:05:40,160
Good thing I didn't let Yan Ying come

90
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:48,920
This scar

91
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:51,120
I don't recall writing about it in my book

92
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,879
but it appeared when I came out of the book

93
00:05:55,519 --> 00:05:56,560
I think the water's almost ready.

94
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:58,959
Editor Xu,

95
00:05:59,319 --> 00:06:00,399
could you help me check the water temperature?

96
00:06:01,439 --> 00:06:02,160
Excuse me?

97
00:06:02,879 --> 00:06:04,399
You want me to check the water temperature for you?

98
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:06,480
How could you even ask that?

99
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,519
Do you really think of me as your servant?

100
00:06:09,480 --> 00:06:11,120
Well, if Editor Xu is unwilling,

101
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,240
and I'm so frail...

102
00:06:12,879 --> 00:06:14,279
I'll just have to manage.

103
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,360
The temperature is just right.

104
00:06:19,920 --> 00:06:20,399
If there's nothing else,

105
00:06:20,399 --> 00:06:21,120
I'll be going now.

106
00:06:21,120 --> 00:06:21,800
Hey, wait a second!

107
00:06:23,680 --> 00:06:24,839
You have that red string as well?

108
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:27,439
I remember Yan Ying also had one when she was little.

109
00:06:31,319 --> 00:06:32,319
But I guess that's not too surprising.

110
00:06:33,439 --> 00:06:35,000
As the author who created us,

111
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,360
you can project all the things you like—

112
00:06:37,879 --> 00:06:39,000
your preferences, emotions,

113
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:41,040
your entire essence onto us.

114
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,199
It's hardly surprising.

115
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,639
For Yan Ying and me,

116
00:06:45,879 --> 00:06:47,560
you have the ultimate power to control everything.

117
00:06:48,480 --> 00:06:50,639
You can alter everything at will based on your preferences.

118
00:06:51,519 --> 00:06:52,800
What exactly are you trying to say?

119
00:06:54,199 --> 00:06:54,959
Xu Chi,

120
00:06:56,199 --> 00:06:57,480
do you truly love Yan Ying?

121
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:00,600
Xiao Chengjing,

122
00:07:02,319 --> 00:07:03,639
did you only like Yan Ying at first sight

123
00:07:04,639 --> 00:07:06,319
because she gave you a sweet cake?

124
00:07:07,439 --> 00:07:09,279
And the first time you drew your sword against her,

125
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:12,319
was it because your ideals mattered more than she did?

126
00:07:14,519 --> 00:07:15,879
Even though I rewrote the ending,

127
00:07:16,959 --> 00:07:18,800
you're still trapped in your character's persona.

128
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:21,959
The only reason I kept you here

129
00:07:22,800 --> 00:07:25,319
was to give you and Yan Ying a fresh start.

130
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:27,360
Hmph.

131
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:30,240
So this is Editor Xu's version of love?

132
00:07:30,839 --> 00:07:32,279
Well, I must experience it thoroughly then.

133
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:33,360
Hey,

134
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,199
look at my shoulder.

135
00:07:35,199 --> 00:07:36,279
The old injury is acting up again.

136
00:07:37,600 --> 00:07:37,879
Give it a massage.

137
00:07:38,639 --> 00:07:38,920
Come on.

138
00:08:05,399 --> 00:08:06,279
Why did I

139
00:08:06,279 --> 00:08:09,399
create such an annoying character in the first place?

140
00:08:10,439 --> 00:08:11,800
But the scar on his arm

141
00:08:12,399 --> 00:08:14,439
why is it exactly the same as the one on Yan Ying's arm?

142
00:08:15,399 --> 00:08:16,319
Even the location is identical.

143
00:08:18,399 --> 00:08:20,079
Could it be that the rewritten storyline

144
00:08:20,959 --> 00:08:22,439
is affecting the previous plot?

145
00:08:25,639 --> 00:08:26,240
Sorry, boss.

146
00:08:26,839 --> 00:08:27,680
It's my fault for not handling it well.

147
00:08:29,639 --> 00:08:29,879
Oh.

148
00:08:30,879 --> 00:08:31,199
It's not your fault.

149
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:33,840
They're targeting me specifically.

150
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:35,559
Boss,

151
00:08:36,360 --> 00:08:37,679
what should we do now?

152
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:42,279
List out the top three online authors from recent rankings.

153
00:08:43,159 --> 00:08:44,519
If we lose one Li Si,

154
00:08:45,200 --> 00:08:47,240
it won't affect our site at all.

155
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:49,360
Understood.
